reviews.review_text:
I am on an amazing journey I am listening to every 1994 show in order, mining for gold. 

Set 1 highlights: All songs played fairly well. 

Set 2 highlights: lackluster, but played well. Drums>Space? 

Decent, but def the last show of the run.
